## Example for item

Item amount -> 100 "التكلفة"
Item Qty -> 1     "الكمية"
-----------------------------
All Customers Data
1) single  "مفرد"
amount -> 50 "المبلغ"
price -> 150 "السعر" (item amount + customer amount)

2) private "خاص"
amount -> 40 "المبلغ"
price -> 140 "السعر" (item amount + customer amount)

3) gomla  "جملة"
amount -> 30 "المبلغ"
price -> 130 "السعر" (item amount + customer amount)

4) G gomla "ج جملة"
amount -> 20 "المبلغ"
price -> 120 "السعر" (item amount + customer amount)
------------------------------------------------------------
## Calculations
qty = 10
additional qty = 5
total qty = qty + additional qty = 15
Discount = 10$


Note : this two cases in which user choose discount as fixed amount or percentage

//TODO:: Case 1
# case 1 (Enable discount from original price)
#### Total price = (customer price * qty) - (discount * qty) ######
//fixed
Total price = (150 * 10) - (10 * 10) = 1,400
//percentage
discount = (customer price * discount)
Total price = (150 * 10) - (15 * 10) = 1,350


####### Price = total price / qty ###########
Price = 1400 / 10 = 140

#### Price For One Piece = Total price / total qty ######
Price For One Piece = 1400 / 15 = 93.33


//TODO:: Case 2
# case 2 (disable discount from original price)
#### Total price = (customer price * qty) - (discount * total qty) ######
Total price = (150 * 10) - (10 * 15) = 1,350

###### Price = total price / total qty ########
Price = 1,350 / 15 = 90

#### Price For One Piece = Total price / total qty ######
Price For One Piece = 1350 / 15 = 90


## implement here other customers depend on the above calculations
customer 2
case 1
total price = (140 * 10) - (10 * 10) = 1,300
price for one piece = 1300 / 15 = 86.67
case 2
total price = (140 * 10) - (10 * 15) = 1,250
price for one piece = 1250 / 15 = 83.33
--------------------------------------------------------

